node.text:
Visit @SculptMovements 💕 for workouts, routine, and everythin else you eed to become fit! .
Treino de MMI com 01. Agachamento máquina 15/12/10 + drop com extensora 4 x 4 / 4x3 / 4x2 /4x 1 aumentando a carga ( 1 série ) 
1 x 10 com pico de contração em cima + 10 saindo da inércia 
1 x 10 com excêntrica lenta + 10 concêntrica lenta + 10 
02. Stiff 3 x 15 + bom dia 10 
03. Flexora 9 x 6 alternando a carga entre leva e pesado 
1 x 30 curtas + 10 isometria + 12 
1 x unilateral 8 /7/6 até zerar sem intervalo 
04. Flexora em pé 3 x 12 parando no meio + glúteo no cabo 3 x 12 
Panturrilhas sempre 😅
Macacão @santtaloren
.
.
.

node.text:
❌Circuit instructions❌

Perform each exercise for ⏰40 seconds

rest ONLY 15 seconds before moving onto the next exercise 😴 Rest 1 min after the last exercise. 🌀3 rounds total .credit : @anita_herbert
.
.
.
#Fitness #fitfam #fitspo #motivation #workout #workoutvideo #legday #gym #abs

TWIST UP CORE WITH THESE MOVES!

Instead of adding abs at the end of my workout,  I will add them to my warmup and  separated within my hour of lifting which allows for more recovery. 

Go till you can’t. Weights help speed up the time it takes for me to go until failure.

3-4x 
Reps no more than 20 or you need to add more weight.  Must keep abs tightly engaged the entire time. 

SUPERSET
1️⃣Decline Bend to Arm Extension
2️⃣Twists 

3️⃣Hanging Sand Bag Leg Raise 
4️⃣Twists then Dropset Twists 

5️⃣Leg Raise Side Twists

WARMUP
6️⃣Ball & 9lb Bar Twists & Raises
•
•
Credit @andreafit4 #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout.

node.text:
HOLIDAY WORKOUT👙🔥 

Ladies you NEED to check out @SculptSwim for summers hottest bikinis 👙 

Beach walk followed by this body weight burnout!

I always say, don’t underestimate what you can do with just your body🥵

1. 30sec Lunges
2. 30sec Explosive Lunges
3. 30sec Step Ups
4. 30sec Explosive Step Ups
2 Rounds (each leg)

1. 20sec Box Jumps
2. 20sec Side Plank Pulses E/S 
3. 20sec Rotated Plank E/S
3 Rounds 

Let me know if you try this, much harder then it looks🔥

16MIN AB CIRCUIT🔥 Save & @SculptMobility for daily pain management, flexibility, and workout advice📚 

Happy weekend, another day in paradise for me👙🌴 

Quick little ab session to start my morning and get moving🔥

1.  30sec Reverse Crunch Complex
2. 30sec Toe Taps
3. 30sec Single Leg Raises 
4. 30sec Oblique Reaches
5. 30sec Bicycles 
6. 30sec Plank
7. 30sec Shoulder Taps
8. 30sec Moving Plank 
4 Rounds

Credit @racheljdillon #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout

node.text:
Put your hands up if you’ve bought a swimsuit subconsciously thinking that SOMEHOW the swimsuit was going to look the same as it did on the girl modeling it. 🙋🏼‍♀️🙅🏼‍♀️ The amount of times I have felt so much shame in my body because this has happened.... the number does not exist lol.

It’s normal to have bumps, marks, and skin that others don’t.
What a boring world it would be if we all looked the same.

So the next time you try on a bathing suit or clothes, it doesn’t fit how you expected, and your inner dialogue is bullying your body— I encourage you to say, “I am not going to expect anything of my body other than showing up as I am”.

Credit @mikzazon

node.text:
Save & visit @EatsConnoisseur for daily delicious foods & recipes to get you slim🥝🍓🍌🍇 

 The viral Greek Pita Bowls are here!! These were a hit at the retreat and a must try! I’ll list the recipe below so make sure to save it!
Via @stayfitmom_krista

For the rice:
1 cup rice + 2 cups water 
1/2 tablespoon turmeric 
1 bay leaf 🍃 
1/4 teaspoon Pepper (leaned this is a must with turmeric on TikTok👍🏻) 

Grill or bake some boneless, skinless chicken thighs. You’ll need 25 ounces of cooked chicken for 5 bowls. 

For the diced veggies:
2 Roma tomatoes (240g) 🍅 
100g red onion
1 cucumber 🥒 

For the bowls:
4 ounces cooked rice
5 ounces cooked chicken thighs 
1/5 diced veggies 
2 tablespoons hummus 
Sprinkle of paprika
4 grams fat free feta (Trader Joe’s)
2 Kalamata olives 

378 cals
34.6p/ 31.3c / 13.9f

20 min AMRAP:
* 18 burpees over bar
* 15 Deadlifts
* 12 hang cleans
* 9 shoulder to OH
* 3 tower runs (up and down 4 flights of stairs + about 100m of straights) 
Barbell weight = 155/105lbs 

Workout from Uncommon CF 

AMRAP = As Many Rounds As Possible (while maintaining good form of course).

Credit @_brialee #abworkout #coreworkout #quadsworkout #legworkout #gluteworkout #workoutvideos  #gymmotivation #bodybuilding #fitnessmotivation #homeworkout #fullbodyworkout #bodyweightworkout
